data.description: Discover the charm of single-story living in this beautiful ranch style home with 2 sheds. Nestled at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. Featuring 4 cozy bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, wired for surround w/speakers (never used as-is), and gas fireplace. This home with a brand new 20 seer GAS HVAC system, underwent a  makeover just six years ago. Upgrades included a new roof, stylish kitchen cabinets, appliances, and elegant granite countertops. Outside, the inviting deck, Gazebo and framing in area for above ground pool, securely enclosed by a fence, offer the perfect retreat for relaxation and entertainment. Conveniently located, this home provides effortless access to the 64 Hi-Rise within just five minutes, blending serene living with ease of travel. $5k Flooring allowance on Full Price Offer.
